            <title><![CDATA[【[哆啦A梦汗]#眼药水每次滴一滴就够了#】滴到眼睛里的眼药水主要存留在下睑结膜囊，结膜囊的容积为10到20微升，而一滴眼药水通常有40到50微升，所以有一滴就足...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦汗]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_04han-372a719d21.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9C%BC%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E6%BB%B4%E4%B8%80%E6%BB%B4%E5%B0%B1%E5%A4%9F%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9C%BC%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E6%BB%B4%E4%B8%80%E6%BB%B4%E5%B0%B1%E5%A4%9F%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#眼药水每次滴一滴就够了#</span></a>】滴到眼睛里的眼药水主要存留在下睑结膜囊，结膜囊的容积为10到20微升，而一滴眼药水通常有40到50微升，所以有一滴就足够了。而且，眼睛并不能吸收过多的眼药水，如果滴的次数过多，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%BB%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E7%9C%BC%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%BB%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E7%9C%BC%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#滴过多眼药水会伤害眼睛#</span></a>，<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>阿卫提醒，滴眼药水不仅要看眼药水的成分，更要遵医嘱<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[上课了]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/0f/2022_Forclass_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6jA2mJW" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
